      "content": "hey so i was cutting veggies and the knife slipped... i have a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s still oozing a bit but it’s not like spraying blood or anything. i dont really want to go to the hospital if i dont have to, do u think i can just clean it and put some honey on it to help it heal faster?",
